#display

value can be:
1.none 
   - hidde the tag
   - hidde the space tage of the work follow  
2. block :
     - tak full width if no width 
     - add line break
     - can accespt padding,margin,width,height
3. inline : 
         - accept padding,margin [just left + right]
         - can not add line break
         - do not take full width
         - make overfollow if padding is big and the next tag is block
         - allow element before and after
4. inline-block
     - allow element before and after
     - can accespt padding,margin,width,height
5. table
-------------------------------------------------------------

visiblity: hidden or visible
   the different between visiblity:hidden th space of tage is stile found after hidded but in display:none the space of 
   tage also well be hidde.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
