#position:
  position:relative;
 has value:
  1. static not efficted by top bottom and leftright
  2. relative depending on top bottom right left property
  3. absolute 
      if the tag is absolute position then depend on parent -should be position:relative- if the parent is not relative 
position go to parent to parent unitl body parent 
   4. fixed
   5. sticky
     depending on top bottom right left well be fixed position when scrolling 
